---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Crescendo Consultants — Independent AI & Technology Consulting"
  description="Fortune 100 AI playbooks delivered directly to your business. Independent strategy and implementation — no agency overhead."
  canonicalPath="/"
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="hero__bg">
      <div class="hero__grid"></div>
      <div class="hero__blob hero__blob--1"></div>
      <div class="hero__blob hero__blob--2"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero__inner">
      <div class="hero__copy">
        <div class="hero__eyebrow">
          <span class="hero__dot"></span>
          Available for new engagements
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero__title">
          Fortune 100 AI playbooks.<br/>
          <span class="hero__title-accent">Delivered directly to your business.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero__subtitle">
          I've spent my career helping some of the world's biggest companies turn AI and data into measurable P&amp;L outcomes. Crescendo brings that same playbook to your team — senior work, directly delivered, no agency overhead.
        </p>
        <div class="hero__cta">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn--primary" data-cal-link="gavin-coleman-pxrlkg/intro" data-cal-namespace="intro" data-cal-config='{"layout":"week_view","useSlotsViewOnSmallScreen":"true"}'>Book a Free Intro Call →</a>
          <a href="#case-studies" class="btn btn--ghost">See Case Studies</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero__stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat__value">8+</div>
            <div class="stat__label">Industries · Fortune 100 Engagements</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat__value">Bain · PS</div>
            <div class="stat__label">Pedigree · Independent Delivery</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat__value">Tailored, Not Templated</div>
            <div class="stat__label">Independent operator. Built for your business.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero__portrait">
        <div class="hero__portrait-frame">
          <img src="/images/hero-main.jpg" alt="Gavin Coleman presenting" />
        </div>
        <div class="hero__badge">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <path d="M10 2L12.5 7L18 8L14 12L15 17.5L10 15L5 17.5L6 12L2 8L7.5 7L10 2Z" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
          Trusted by founders & operators
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- LOGO BAR -->
  <section class="logos">
    <p class="logos__label">Worked with teams at</p>
    <div class="logos__grid logos__grid--images">
      <div class="logos__item-img"><img src="/images/logos/disney.svg" alt="Disney" /></div>
      <div class="logos__item-img"><img src="/images/logos/marriott.svg" alt="Marriott" /></div>
      <div class="logos__item-img"><img src="/images/logos/walmart.svg" alt="Walmart" /></div>
      <div class="logos__item-img"><img src="/images/logos/dsg.svg" alt="Dick's Sporting Goods" /></div>
      <div class="logos__item-img"><img src="/images/logos/colgate.svg" alt="Colgate" /></div>
      <div class="logos__item-img"><img src="/images/logos/publicissapient.svg" alt="Publicis Sapient" /></div>
      <div class="logos__item-img"><img src="/images/logos/amex.svg" alt="American Express" /></div>
      <div class="logos__item-img"><img src="/images/logos/citi.svg" alt="Citi" /></div>
      <div class="logos__item-img"><img src="/images/logos/morganstanley.svg" alt="Morgan Stanley" /></div>
      <div class="logos__item-img"><img src="/images/logos/marcus.svg" alt="Marcus by Goldman Sachs" /></div>
      <div class="logos__item-img"><img src="/images/logos/fidelity.svg" alt="Fidelity" /></div>
      <div class="logos__item-img"><img src="/images/logos/santander.svg" alt="Santander" /></div>
      <div class="logos__item-img"><img src="/images/logos/bain.svg" alt="Bain &amp; Company" /></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section id="about" class="about section">
    <div class="section__inner about__inner">
      <div class="about__photo">
        <div class="about__photo-frame">
          <img src="/images/about-portrait.jpg" alt="Gavin Coleman" />
        </div>
        <div class="about__photo-accent"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="about__content">
        <div class="eyebrow">About</div>
        <h2 class="section__title">
          Enterprise pattern recognition.<br/>
          Independent delivery.
        </h2>
        <p class="about__text">
          I started my career in high-stakes private equity, where I developed the analytical discipline and decision-making instincts that still shape how I approach every engagement. From there I moved into management consulting and eventually into a senior role leading Data &amp; AI strategy for enterprise clients. Across all three, the through-line has been the same: learning how capital allocators, operators, and technologists actually think — and translating between them.
        </p>
        <p class="about__text">
          I've led enterprise-scale AI and digital transformation programs across financial services, retail, hospitality, and entertainment — turning AI strategy into operational reality for Fortune 100 teams. My work spans the full arc: C-suite roadmaps and competitive assessments through hands-on implementation of agentic AI systems, data infrastructure, and intelligent automation.
        </p>
        <p class="about__text">
          I'm trained in both business strategy and modern technical execution — Python, SQL, cloud platforms, and the full agentic AI stack. I can present to the board in the morning and ship production code by that afternoon. That combination is rare, and it's why every engagement I take moves faster than a traditional consulting project.
        </p>
        <p class="about__text">
          Today I keep my client list deliberately small. When you hire Crescendo, you hire me — not a delivery team. That means you get the exact same thinking, the exact same code, from first call to final system. Here's how that works in practice:
        </p>
        <div class="about__highlights">
          <div class="highlight">
            <div class="highlight__icon">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3c0 1.6.8 3 2 3.9V12l-7 3v4l7-2v2.5l-2 2V23l3-1 3 1v-1.5l-2-2V17l7 2v-4l-7-3V8.9c1.2-.9 2-2.3 2-3.9a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="highlight__title">Discovery First</div>
              <div class="highlight__desc">I personally diagnose your bottlenecks and opportunities before recommending a single thing</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight">
            <div class="highlight__icon">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="highlight__title">Modern Methods &amp; Tools</div>
              <div class="highlight__desc">Agentic AI, Python, cloud — the Fortune 100 stack, right-sized for your business</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight">
            <div class="highlight__icon">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3v18h18"/><path d="M18.7 8l-5.1 5.2-2.8-2.7L7 14.3"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="highlight__title">Financial Rigor</div>
              <div class="highlight__desc">Every rec justified by the P&amp;L</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight">
            <div class="highlight__icon">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="highlight__title">Exclusive Partnership</div>
              <div class="highlight__desc">You work with me directly — no handoffs, no templates, no rotating faces</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section id="services" class="services section section--dark">
    <div class="section__inner">
      <div class="section__header">
        <div class="eyebrow eyebrow--light">Services</div>
        <h2 class="section__title section__title--light">
          Six ways I help businesses grow.
        </h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">
          Every engagement is tailored, but most fall into one of these areas. Need something else? Let's talk.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="services__grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2l3 7 7 .6-5.3 4.8L18 22l-6-3.5L6 22l1.3-7.6L2 9.6 9 9z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__num">01</div>
          <h3 class="service-card__title">AI Strategy &amp; Implementation</h3>
          <p class="service-card__desc">Identify your highest-leverage AI opportunities and deliver them end-to-end. From discovery to deployment to measurable ROI.</p>
          <ul class="service-card__list">
            <li>AI opportunity assessment</li>
            <li>Custom GPT &amp; Claude integrations</li>
            <li>Implementation &amp; change management</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><path d="M9 13h6M9 17h6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__num">02</div>
          <h3 class="service-card__title">Intelligent Automation</h3>
          <p class="service-card__desc">Turn repetitive operational work into automated workflows. Free your team to focus on the work that actually drives growth.</p>
          <ul class="service-card__list">
            <li>Workflow automation design</li>
            <li>Custom tool &amp; integration builds</li>
            <li>Process redesign &amp; optimization</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__num">03</div>
          <h3 class="service-card__title">Reputation &amp; Customer Intelligence</h3>
          <p class="service-card__desc">AI-powered systems that monitor your reviews, surface customer insights, and help you respond at scale — before problems compound.</p>
          <ul class="service-card__list">
            <li>Review monitoring &amp; sentiment analysis</li>
            <li>Automated response systems</li>
            <li>Competitive positioning dashboards</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__num">04</div>
          <h3 class="service-card__title">Custom AI Tools</h3>
          <p class="service-card__desc">Bespoke chatbots, assistants, and analytics tools built around your exact business logic. Not templates — real systems.</p>
          <ul class="service-card__list">
            <li>Internal knowledge assistants</li>
            <li>Customer-facing AI chatbots</li>
            <li>Bespoke analytics dashboards</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M3 5v14a9 3 0 0 0 18 0V5"/><path d="M3 12a9 3 0 0 0 18 0"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__num">05</div>
          <h3 class="service-card__title">Data Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="service-card__desc">From spreadsheets to scalable data systems. Design the foundations your team needs to make data-driven decisions as you grow.</p>
          <ul class="service-card__list">
            <li>Data architecture &amp; modeling</li>
            <li>ETL pipelines &amp; reporting</li>
            <li>Migration from legacy systems</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__num">06</div>
          <h3 class="service-card__title">Fractional Technology Leadership</h3>
          <p class="service-card__desc">Strategic tech guidance without the cost of a full-time CTO. Available as a retainer for ongoing leadership and decision support.</p>
          <ul class="service-card__list">
            <li>Tech roadmap &amp; architecture</li>
            <li>Vendor evaluation &amp; negotiation</li>
            <li>Team coaching &amp; hiring support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CASE STUDIES -->
  <section id="case-studies" class="cases section">
    <div class="section__inner">
      <div class="section__header section__header--center">
        <div class="eyebrow">Case Studies</div>
        <h2 class="section__title">Real clients. Real numbers. Real outcomes.</h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">The Fortune 100 pattern library, applied to mid-market problems. Every case below is a real client, with real results.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cases__grid">
        <article class="case-card">
          <div class="case-card__tag">Healthcare · Reputation</div>
          <h3 class="case-card__title">Reputation Intelligence for a Manhattan Dental Practice</h3>
          <p class="case-card__desc">Built a custom AI reputation audit system that pulls reviews across platforms, runs sentiment analysis, and generates actionable recommendations — turning weeks of manual work into a 90-second automated process.</p>
          <div class="case-card__metrics">
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">+40%</div><div class="metric__label">5-star review rate</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">15 hrs</div><div class="metric__label">Saved per week</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">89</div><div class="metric__label">Health score (up from 62)</div></div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="case-card">
          <div class="case-card__tag">SaaS · HR Tech</div>
          <h3 class="case-card__title">AI-Powered HR Policy Assistant</h3>
          <p class="case-card__desc">Deployed a Claude-powered internal chatbot that ingests employee handbooks and HR policies, then answers employee questions in natural language 24/7 with citations to the source policy.</p>
          <div class="case-card__metrics">
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">80%</div><div class="metric__label">HR questions self-served</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">6 hrs</div><div class="metric__label">HR time recovered weekly</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">85</div><div class="metric__label">Employees served</div></div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="case-card">
          <div class="case-card__tag">Private Equity · M&amp;A · Intelligent Automation</div>
          <h3 class="case-card__title">Operational Diligence Agent for a Mid-Market PE Fund</h3>
          <p class="case-card__desc">Built an AI diligence system for an $800M mid-market PE fund that ingests target financials, org charts, and operational data, then generates a 40-page operational diligence memo in two hours — work that previously took analysts three weeks per deal.</p>
          <div class="case-card__metrics">
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">$600K</div><div class="metric__label">Diligence cost saved (8 deals)</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">93%</div><div class="metric__label">Analyst time reclaimed</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">2 deals</div><div class="metric__label">Killed on AI-flagged risk</div></div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="case-card">
          <div class="case-card__tag">Professional Services · Automation</div>
          <h3 class="case-card__title">Automated Customer Onboarding Pipeline</h3>
          <p class="case-card__desc">Replaced a manual 3-day customer onboarding process with an automated pipeline that handles contract intake, data collection, kickoff scheduling, and resource provisioning — all triggered by a single form submission.</p>
          <div class="case-card__metrics">
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">-93%</div><div class="metric__label">Onboarding time (3 days → 2 hrs)</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">100%</div><div class="metric__label">Error-free handoffs</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">4.9★</div><div class="metric__label">Client onboarding NPS</div></div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="case-card case-card--featured">
          <div class="case-card__tag">Healthcare · Agentic Workflows</div>
          <h3 class="case-card__title">AI-Powered Patient Intake for a Multi-Site Medical Group</h3>
          <p class="case-card__desc">Built an AI voice and chat intake agent for an 8-clinic medical group that captures insurance, medical history, and visit prep before the patient arrives — replacing a manual 45-minute process and delivering handoff-ready context to clinical staff in under 10 minutes.</p>
          <div class="case-card__metrics">
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">-78%</div><div class="metric__label">Intake time (45 min → 10 min)</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">+$1.2M</div><div class="metric__label">Annual patient capacity</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="metric__value">94%</div><div class="metric__label">Pre-visit completion rate</div></div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section id="testimonials" class="testimonials section section--subtle">
    <div class="section__inner">
      <div class="section__header section__header--center">
        <div class="eyebrow">Testimonials</div>
        <h2 class="section__title">What clients say.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonials__grid">
        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial__stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial__quote">
            "Gavin transformed how we think about our online presence. He didn't just hand us a report — he built a system we actually use every day. The ROI was clear within the first month."
          </p>
          <footer class="testimonial__author">
            <div class="testimonial__avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6366f1,#8b5cf6);">SC</div>
            <div><div class="testimonial__name">Sarah Chen</div><div class="testimonial__role">CEO, Manhattan Dental Group</div></div>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial__stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial__quote">
            "Gavin is the rare consultant who can think strategically and actually ship code. He understood our business in two meetings and delivered something our engineering team couldn't build in six months."
          </p>
          <footer class="testimonial__author">
            <div class="testimonial__avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#10b981,#06b6d4);">MW</div>
            <div><div class="testimonial__name">Marcus Weber</div><div class="testimonial__role">Founder, Horizon Technologies</div></div>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial__stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial__quote">
            "Working with Gavin felt like having a senior partner from a top-tier firm in our corner — without the political games or inflated invoices. He's direct, fast, and genuinely invested in outcomes."
          </p>
          <footer class="testimonial__author">
            <div class="testimonial__avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f59e0b,#ef4444);">PP</div>
            <div><div class="testimonial__name">Priya Patel</div><div class="testimonial__role">COO, Apex Advisory Partners</div></div>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial__stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial__quote">
            "We hired Gavin for a two-week AI assessment and ended up extending the engagement for six months. He identified automation opportunities we'd missed for years — and then actually built them."
          </p>
          <footer class="testimonial__author">
            <div class="testimonial__avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#8b5cf6,#ec4899);">DK</div>
            <div><div class="testimonial__name">David Kim</div><div class="testimonial__role">VP Operations, Nimbus Logistics</div></div>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial__stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial__quote">
            "The combination of financial acumen from his M&amp;A background and real technology chops is unusual. He speaks our investors' language and our engineers' language. That's rare."
          </p>
          <footer class="testimonial__author">
            <div class="testimonial__avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#06b6d4,#3b82f6);">JR</div>
            <div><div class="testimonial__name">Jessica Rodriguez</div><div class="testimonial__role">CEO, Brightline SaaS</div></div>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial__stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial__quote">
            "Gavin is my go-to whenever we need to evaluate new technology or build an internal tool. He's saved us from two bad vendor decisions and built three tools that are now core to our operations."
          </p>
          <footer class="testimonial__author">
            <div class="testimonial__avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ef4444,#f59e0b);">RT</div>
            <div><div class="testimonial__name">Ryan Thompson</div><div class="testimonial__role">Managing Partner, Keystone Ventures</div></div>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT / CTA -->
  <section id="contact" class="contact section section--cta">
    <div class="contact__bg">
      <div class="contact__blob"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section__inner contact__inner">
      <div class="eyebrow eyebrow--light">Let's Talk</div>
      <h2 class="contact__title">
        Worth 30 minutes of your time?<br/>
        <span class="contact__title-accent">Let's find out.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="contact__subtitle">
        Book an intro call. I work with a small number of clients at a time — I'll tell you honestly whether I can help.
      </p>
      <div class="contact__actions">
        <a class="btn btn--primary btn--large" data-cal-link="gavin-coleman-pxrlkg/intro" data-cal-namespace="intro" data-cal-config='{"layout":"week_view","useSlotsViewOnSmallScreen":"true"}'>Book a Free Intro Call →</a>
        <a href="mailto:Gavin-Coleman@crescendo-consulting.net?subject=Consulting%20inquiry" class="btn btn--ghost btn--large">Email Me</a>
      </div>
      <div class="contact__direct">
        <a href="mailto:Gavin-Coleman@crescendo-consulting.net">Gavin-Coleman@crescendo-consulting.net</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
